@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Company Profile";
}

<style>
    /* ── HERO SECTION ── */
    .cp-hero {
        position: relative;
        width: 100vw;
        margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
        height: 380px;
        overflow: hidden;
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-end;
        padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .cp-hero-bg {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: url('/images/image slide 4.jpg') center center / cover no-repeat;
        filter: brightness(0.85);
        transform: scale(1.03);
        transition: transform 8s ease;
    }

    .cp-hero:hover .cp-hero-bg {
        transform: scale(1.0);
    }

    .cp-hero-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(10,20,50,0.2) 0%, rgba(10,20,50,0.75) 100%);
    }

    .cp-hero-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        padding: 0 2rem;
        max-width: 1140px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .cp-breadcrumb {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #60a5fa;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .cp-hero-title {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        line-height: 1.15;
        margin: 0;
    }

    /* ── CONTENT SECTION ── */
    .cp-content-wrapper {
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
        margin-top: -2rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 3;
        box-shadow: 0 -4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        padding: 3rem 2rem 4rem;
        max-width: 1140px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        width: 100%;
    }

    /* ── CHANGED: stack image on top, content below ── */
    .cp-grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    /* Left: Text */
    .cp-text-col {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 860px;
    }

    .cp-lead-heading {
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1e293b;
        line-height: 1.4;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
        padding-left: 1rem;
    }

    .cp-body-text {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #4b5563;
        line-height: 1.85;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .cp-divider {
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        margin: 1.75rem 0;
    }

    /* Vessel service tags */
    .cp-tags {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .cp-tag {
        background: #eff6ff;
        color: #dc2626;
        border: 1px solid #dc2626;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    /* ── CHANGED: image column now full-width centered ── */
    .cp-image-col {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 860px;
        position: static;
    }

    .cp-img-main {
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 12px;
        object-fit: cover;
        height: 420px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        display: block;
    }

    .cp-img-caption {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #9ca3af;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 0.6rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    /* Stats row */
    .cp-stats {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        padding-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .cp-stat {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .cp-stat-number {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: #1a365d;
        line-height: 1;
        display: block;
    }

    .cp-stat-label {
        font-size: 11px;
        color: #6b7280;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
        font-weight: 500;
        margin-top: 0.3rem;
        display: block;
    }

    /* ── DIRECTORS SECTION ── */
    .dir-section {
        margin-top: 4rem;
        padding-top: 3rem;
    }

    .dir-section-label {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #2563eb;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .dir-section-title {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1e293b;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .dir-section-subtitle {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #6b7280;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        max-width: 540px;
    }

    .dir-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 3rem;
        align-items: start;
    }

    .dir-card {
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: visible;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

        .dir-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }

    .dir-card-img-wrap {
        width: 100%;
        height: 380px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }

        .dir-card-img-wrap img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: top center;
            display: block;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

    .dir-card:hover .dir-card-img-wrap img {
        transform: scale(1.03);
    }

    .dir-card-body {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 1.75rem 0.25rem 2rem;
        border-top: 3px solid #dc2626;
        margin-top: 1.25rem;
    }

    .dir-name {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1e293b;
        margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .dir-role {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #2563eb;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .dir-bio {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #4b5563;
        line-height: 1.85;
    }

    /* ── Fun "fun fact" highlight pill inside director cards ── */
    .dir-highlight {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        background: #f0fdf4;
        border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
        color: #15803d;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

        .dir-highlight::before {
            content: "⚓";
            font-size: 12px;
        }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .cp-hero {
            height: 280px;
        }

        .cp-img-main {
            height: 240px;
        }

        .cp-content-wrapper {
            padding: 2rem 1.25rem 3rem;
        }

        .dir-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .dir-card-img-wrap {
            height: 280px;
        }
    }
</style>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<div class="cp-hero">
    <div class="cp-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="cp-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="cp-hero-content">
        <p class="cp-breadcrumb">About Us / Company Overview</p>
        <h1 class="cp-hero-title">Company Overview</h1>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- ── MAIN CONTENT ── -->
<div class="cp-content-wrapper">
    <div class="cp-grid">

        <!-- TOP: Image (moved above text) -->
        <div class="cp-image-col">
            <p class="cp-lead-heading">
                Synergy Marine (M) Sdn Bhd was established on 2012 as a Bumiputera company.
            </p>
            <video src="/videos/FINAL.mp4" class="cp-img-main" autoplay muted loop playsinline></video>
            <p class="cp-img-caption">MV Synergy Aurora — part of our operational fleet</p>
        </div>

        <!-- BOTTOM: Text -->
        <div class="cp-text-col">


            <p class="cp-body-text">
                We are registered company under Companies Commission of Malaysia (1019421-T) and Ministry of Finance
                that specialized in rendering customized products and services to the oil &amp; gas industry.
            </p>

            <p class="cp-body-text">
                We provide comprehensive vessel services including:
            </p>

            <div class="cp-tags">
                <span class="cp-tag">Anchor Handling Tug Supply Vessel (AHTS)</span>
                <span class="cp-tag">Platform Supply Vessel (PSV)</span>
                <span class="cp-tag">Straight Supply Vessel (SSV)</span>
                <span class="cp-tag">Utility Vessel (UV)</span>
                <span class="cp-tag">Safety Standby Vessel (SV)</span>
                <span class="cp-tag">Diving Support Vessel (DSV)</span>
                <span class="cp-tag">Accommodation Workboat / Workbarge (AWB)</span>
            </div>

            <p class="cp-body-text">
                We are able to provide comprehensive service with combined experience of the management team.
            </p>

            <p class="cp-body-text">
                Besides that, we also have clients in offshore engineering and services contractors, ship owners and
                managers, logistic support companies, yards, drilling and offshore services companies and general
                offshore contractors. We are committed to provide good service to our clients.
            </p>

            <p class="cp-body-text">
                In Synergy Marine (M) Sdn Bhd, our management team has a significant number of years of experience
                in the marine services industry. This allows us to provide our clients with the most appropriate
                offshore support vessel and other services.
            </p>

            <!-- Stats -->
            <div class="cp-stats">
                <div class="cp-stat">
                    <span class="cp-stat-number">2012</span>
                    <span class="cp-stat-label">Established</span>
                </div>
                <div class="cp-stat">
                    <span class="cp-stat-number">7+</span>
                    <span class="cp-stat-label">Vessel Types</span>
                </div>
                <div class="cp-stat">
                    <span class="cp-stat-number">O&G</span>
                    <span class="cp-stat-label">Industry Focus</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- ── DIRECTORS SECTION ── -->
    <div class="dir-section">
        <center>
            <p class="dir-section-label">Leadership</p>
            <h2 class="dir-section-title">Meet the Captains of the Ship </h2>
            <p class="dir-section-subtitle">
                Every great voyage needs a great crew at the helm. Meet the experienced duo steering Synergy Marine
                through the waves of the oil &amp; gas industry — decade after decade.
            </p>
        </center>
        <div class="dir-grid">

            <!-- Director 1 -->
            <div class="dir-card">
                <div class="dir-card-img-wrap">
                    <img src="/images/Dato-Dr-Roslan-Ahmad.jpg" alt="Dato' Dr. Roslan Ahmad" />
                </div>
                <div class="dir-card-body">
                    <span class="dir-highlight">34+ Years at Sea (Industry-wise!)</span>
                    <p class="dir-name">Dato' Dr. Roslan Ahmad</p>
                    <p class="dir-role">Managing Director & Founder</p>
                    <p class="dir-bio">
                        The man who started it all. YBhg. Dato' Dr. Roslan Bin Ahmad is a seasoned entrepreneur with
                        over 34 years across developments, engineering, transportation, services, and maritime. Since
                        2002, he has been deeply embedded in OSV chartering and operations — serving major oil companies
                        across Malaysia, Thailand, and the Middle East.
                    </p>
                    <p class="dir-bio" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
                        Beyond Synergy Marine, he's an active voice in the industry: Vice President of MOSVA
                        (Malaysia OSV Owners' Association) 2025/2026, lifetime member of MASTRA, and a member of
                        IAMSP (UK), IMSML, and the Malaysia Norway Business Council. Basically, if there's a room
                        where maritime decisions are being made — he's in it.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Director 2 -->
            <div class="dir-card">
                <div class="dir-card-img-wrap">
                    <img src="/images/Mohd-Asmawi-Ilias.jpg" alt="Mohd Asmawi Ilias" />
                </div>
                <div class="dir-card-body">
                    <span class="dir-highlight">20+ Years in Oil & Gas Finance</span>
                    <p class="dir-name">Mohd Asmawi Ilias</p>
                    <p class="dir-role">Finance Director</p>
                    <p class="dir-bio">
                        The financial backbone of Synergy Marine. With over 20 years of experience in the oil and gas
                        industry and a 50% stake in the company, Mohd Asmawi doesn't just manage the numbers — he
                        owns them. From accounting and treasury to taxation, audit, and investor relations, he keeps
                        the company's financial engines running smooth.
                    </p>
                    <p class="dir-bio" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
                        But his role doesn't stop at the spreadsheet. He also oversees facilities and overall
                        operations, making sure the whole organization runs like a well-oiled (pun intended) machine.
                        The kind of person who makes sure the ship is always stocked before it sets sail.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

</div>